content: There are millions of 'closet' Trump supporters out there; more than in 2016 and it's exactly why we vote on a secret ballot. ,#,WalkAway, ,#,DemExit, because ,#,NeoLiberalismSucks

I'm mostly indifferent in terms of Trump,I revile Mike Pence though. Trump I dont agree with much but so far every Dem who's been paraded out as "a winner"I want in federal prison so my plan is ,#,MegillaGorilla2020, If I meet nice Trump supporters in person, warning I may hug them.

& I'm really sickened by the abuse& attacks faced by individual people based upon which political candidate or office holder they support. I put in my ballot for Jill Stein &if I saw that in person- Trump supporter attacked-I'd at least try to help them in any &every way I could!

I remember1day wearing my "Make America READ Again" hat- getting almost every1 in a bus I was on singing/jeering "yay for Trump& you white Supremacists" fearing I'd get mugged. Some clowns are so enraged that they will kill supporters of his--A late mentor of mine was a supporter

She put in her ballot for him & died in the hospice she was in shortly before the inauguration - I didn't stop loving said woman over her choice - your ballot your choice - if it really was "only Trump vs Clinton" no questions asked- I'd have chosen Trump!
